<paragraph blockId="0.[151,542,1344,1370]" box="[151,542,1344,1370]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">
<heading bold="true" box="[151,542,1344,1370]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" reason="1">
<taxonomicName box="[151,542,1344,1370]" class="Amphibia" family="Hynobiidae" genus="Pseudohynobius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caudata" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="shuichengensis">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,542,1344,1370]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">Pseudohynobius shuichengensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[151,1436,1413,2026]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">
This species was first described by Tian Yingzhou, Gu Xiaomin, Sun Aiqun &amp; Li Shong (
<number box="[1151,1206,1413,1436]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="1998.0">1998</number>
) in the 
<emphasis box="[1297,1356,1413,1436]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">
<collectionCode box="[1297,1356,1413,1436]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">JLTC</collectionCode>
</emphasis>
. In the original description, the 
<typeStatus box="[419,512,1448,1471]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">holotype</typeStatus>
was stated to be the adult male 
<collectionCode box="[875,942,1448,1471]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">LTHC</collectionCode>
<number box="[952,1045,1448,1471]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="9460080.0">9460080</number>
(total length 
<quantity box="[1196,1309,1448,1471]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.957" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" unit="mm" value="195.7">195.7 mm</quantity>
, snout-vent length 103.0 mm) collected on 
<date box="[502,650,1483,1506]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="1994-06-11">
<number box="[502,528,1483,1506]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="11.0">11</number>
June 
<number box="[597,650,1483,1506]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="1994.0">1994</number>
</date>
at an elevation of 
<number box="[866,919,1483,1506]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="1820.0">1820</number>
metres in the Shuicheng County. The original description also mentioned an ‘allotype’ female 
<collectionCode box="[684,751,1517,1540]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">LTHC</collectionCode>
<number box="[761,854,1517,1540]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="9460084.0">9460084</number>
collected at the same time and place, and 
<number box="[1331,1371,1517,1540]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="100.0">100</number>
other 
<typeStatus box="[151,253,1552,1575]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">paratypes</typeStatus>
(
<specimenCount box="[267,365,1552,1575]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" type="male">
<number box="[267,294,1552,1575]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="10.0">10</number>
males
</specimenCount>
, 
<specimenCount box="[375,494,1552,1575]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" type="female">
<number box="[375,402,1552,1575]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="10.0">10</number>
females
</specimenCount>
, 
<number box="[503,530,1552,1575]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="80.0">80</number>
young) collected from 
<number box="[777,916,1552,1575]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="1995.5" valueMax="1997.0" valueMin="1994.0">
<date box="[777,916,1552,1575]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="1994" valueMax="1997">1994 to 1997</date>
</number>
between 
<date box="[1017,1174,1552,1575]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="1800" valueMax="1850">
<number box="[1017,1070,1552,1575]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="1800.0">1800</number>
and 
<number box="[1121,1174,1552,1575]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="1850.0">1850</number>
</date>
metres in the Shuicheng County. 
<bibRefCitation author="Dubois" box="[243,458,1587,1610]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" refString="Dubois, A., Crombie, R. I. &amp; Glaw, F. (2005) Amphibia Mundi. 1.2. Recent amphibians: generic and infrageneric taxonomic additions (1981 - 2002). Alytes, 23 (1 - 2), 25 - 69." type="journal article" year="2005">
Dubois 
<emphasis box="[328,384,1587,1610]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">et al.</emphasis>
(
<number box="[400,458,1587,1610]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="2005.0">2005</number>
</bibRefCitation>
: 
<number box="[470,498,1587,1610]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="48.0">48</number>
) noted that the specific epithet appeared under three different spellings in the original publication (
<taxonomicName box="[293,454,1621,1644]" class="Amphibia" family="Hynobiidae" genus="Pseudohynobius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caudata" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="shuichengensis">
<emphasis box="[293,454,1621,1644]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">shuichengensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[475,637,1621,1644]" class="Amphibia" family="Hynobiidae" genus="Pseudohynobius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caudata" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="xhuichengensis">
<emphasis box="[475,637,1621,1644]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">xhuichengensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis box="[659,807,1621,1644]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">shuichenensis</emphasis>
), and, acting as first revisers, they chose the spelling 
<taxonomicName box="[151,312,1656,1679]" class="Amphibia" family="Hynobiidae" genus="Pseudohynobius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caudata" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="shuichengensis">
<emphasis box="[151,312,1656,1679]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">shuichengensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as the ‘correct original spelling’ of the nomen. 
<bibRefCitation author="Frost" box="[829,962,1656,1679]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" refString="Frost, D. (2014) Amphibian species of the world: an online reference. Version 6.0. New York, American Museum of Natural History. Available from: http: // research. amnh. org / herpetology / amphibia / (accessed 18 March 2015)" type="journal article" year="2014">
Frost (
<number box="[899,955,1656,1679]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="2014.0">2014</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
credited in error this original description to ‘ 
<bibRefCitation author="Tian" box="[155,382,1691,1714]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" refString="Tian, Y., Gu, X., Sun, A. &amp; Li, S. (1998) A new species of Pseudohynobius guizhouensys (Caudaa: Hynbiidae) - Pseudohynobius xhuichengensis sp. nov. [sic]. Journal of Liupanshui Teachers College, 1998 (4), 7 - 13. [in Chinese with English abstract]" type="journal article" year="1998">
Tian, Li &amp; Gu, 
<number box="[324,382,1691,1714]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="1998.0">1998</number>
</bibRefCitation>
’ and stated that the 
<typeStatus box="[593,686,1691,1714]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">holotype</typeStatus>
was 
<collectionCode box="[741,808,1691,1714]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">LTHC</collectionCode>
<number box="[815,911,1691,1714]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="9460084.0">9460084</number>
, but this is the number of the ‘allotype’.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[151,1436,1413,2026]" lastBlockId="1.[151,1436,152,279]" lastPageId="1" lastPageNumber="596" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">
<bibRefCitation box="[199,430,1725,1748]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" refString="Tian, Y. - Z., Li, S. &amp; Gu, X. - M. (2006) A new species of genus Pseudohynobius (Caudata: Hynobiidae) - Pseudohynobius shuichengensis. Acta zoologica sinica, 52 (3), 522 - 527. [in Chinese with English abstract]" type="journal article">
Tian, Li &amp; Gu (
<number box="[366,422,1725,1748]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="2006.0">2006</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
redescribed this species in 
<emphasis box="[725,963,1725,1748]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">Acta Zoologica Sinica</emphasis>
under the same nomen, without mentioning the original description. They therefore created a new nomen, having a different authorship and date and being an invalid junior homonym of the original nomen (for details see 
<bibRefCitation author="Dubois" box="[769,914,1795,1818]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" refString="Dubois, A. (2012) The distinction between introduction of a new nomen and subsequent use of a previously introduced nomen in zoological nomenclature. Bionomina, 5, 57 - 80. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.11646 / bionomina. 5.1.2" type="journal article" year="2012">
Dubois 
<number box="[856,914,1795,1818]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="2012.0">2012</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). They gave the same information for the 
<typeStatus box="[1390,1436,1795,1818]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">type</typeStatus>
specimens, including their numbers and measurements (except for the total length of the 
<typeStatus box="[1107,1203,1829,1852]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">holotype</typeStatus>
, given as 
<quantity box="[1311,1423,1829,1852]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.975" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" unit="mm" value="197.5">197.5 mm</quantity>
), but they changed the figures for the elevations of the collection of the 
<typeStatus box="[911,1004,1864,1887]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">holotype</typeStatus>
and ‘allotype’ (
<number box="[1177,1232,1864,1887]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="1970.0">1970</number>
metres) and of the other 
<typeStatus box="[212,314,1899,1922]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">paratypes</typeStatus>
(
<number box="[329,450,1899,1922]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="1940.0" valueMax="1970.0" valueMin="1910.0">1910–1970</number>
metres). 
<bibRefCitation author="Frost" box="[550,682,1899,1922]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" refString="Frost, D. (2014) Amphibian species of the world: an online reference. Version 6.0. New York, American Museum of Natural History. Available from: http: // research. amnh. org / herpetology / amphibia / (accessed 18 March 2015)" type="journal article" year="2014">
Frost (
<number box="[619,675,1899,1922]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="2014.0">2014</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
gave the latter figures for the original description, although they seem to be a ‘correction’ (without explanation) of the original data. 
<bibRefCitation author="Frost" box="[841,975,1933,1956]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" refString="Frost, D. (2014) Amphibian species of the world: an online reference. Version 6.0. New York, American Museum of Natural History. Available from: http: // research. amnh. org / herpetology / amphibia / (accessed 18 March 2015)" type="journal article" year="2014">
Frost (
<number box="[912,968,1933,1956]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="2014.0">2014</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
stated that the 
<typeStatus box="[1148,1241,1933,1956]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">holotype</typeStatus>
mentioned in the redescription (
<collectionCode box="[310,379,1968,1991]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">LTHC</collectionCode>
<number box="[392,487,1968,1991]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="9460080.0">9460080</number>
) was a different specimen from the original one, which would make both nomina subjective synonyms (doxisonyms). In fact, the nomen 
<taxonomicName authority="Tian, Li &amp; Gu, 2006" authorityName="Tian, Li &amp; Gu" authorityYear="2006" box="[737,1302,2003,2026]" class="Amphibia" family="Hynobiidae" genus="Pseudohynobius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caudata" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="shuichengensis">
<emphasis box="[737,1080,2003,2026]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">Pseudohynobius shuichengensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Tian" box="[1086,1302,2003,2026]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" refString="Tian, Y. - Z., Li, S. &amp; Gu, X. - M. (2006) A new species of genus Pseudohynobius (Caudata: Hynobiidae) - Pseudohynobius shuichengensis. Acta zoologica sinica, 52 (3), 522 - 527. [in Chinese with English abstract]" type="journal article" year="2006">
Tian, Li &amp; Gu, 
<number box="[1249,1302,2003,2026]" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" value="2006.0">2006</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is simply an invalid objective junior synonym (isonym) of 
<taxonomicName authority="Tian, Gu, Sun &amp; Li, 1998" authorityName="Tian, Gu, Sun &amp; Li" authorityYear="1998" box="[667,1322,152,175]" class="Amphibia" family="Hynobiidae" genus="Pseudohynobius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caudata" pageId="1" pageNumber="596" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="shuichengensis">
<emphasis box="[667,1014,152,175]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="596">Pseudohynobius shuichengensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Tian" box="[1025,1322,152,175]" pageId="1" pageNumber="596" refString="Tian, Y., Gu, X., Sun, A. &amp; Li, S. (1998) A new species of Pseudohynobius guizhouensys (Caudaa: Hynbiidae) - Pseudohynobius xhuichengensis sp. nov. [sic]. Journal of Liupanshui Teachers College, 1998 (4), 7 - 13. [in Chinese with English abstract]" type="journal article" year="1998">
Tian, Gu, Sun &amp; Li, 
<number box="[1266,1322,152,175]" pageId="1" pageNumber="596" value="1998.0">1998</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. This was acknowledged by 
<bibRefCitation author="Fei" box="[348,521,186,209]" pageId="1" pageNumber="596" refString="Fei, L., Hu, S., Ye, C. &amp; Huang, Y. (2009) Fauna Sinica. Amphibia. 3. Anura Ranidae. Beijing, Science Press, [i - iii] + i - xii + 959 - 1847, pl. 1 - 16. [In Chinese]." type="journal article" year="2009">
Fei 
<emphasis box="[391,447,186,209]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="596">et al.</emphasis>
(
<number box="[463,521,186,209]" pageId="1" pageNumber="596" value="2009.0">2009</number>
</bibRefCitation>
: 
<number box="[533,589,186,209]" pageId="1" pageNumber="596" value="1611.0">1611</number>
). This nomen appears also under two spellings in the paper of 
<bibRefCitation pageId="1" pageNumber="596" refString="Tian, Y. - Z., Li, S. &amp; Gu, X. - M. (2006) A new species of genus Pseudohynobius (Caudata: Hynobiidae) - Pseudohynobius shuichengensis. Acta zoologica sinica, 52 (3), 522 - 527. [in Chinese with English abstract]" type="journal article">
Tian, Li &amp; Gu (
<number box="[159,218,221,244]" pageId="1" pageNumber="596" value="2006.0">2006</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
: 
<taxonomicName box="[241,402,221,244]" class="Amphibia" family="Hynobiidae" genus="Pseudohynobius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caudata" pageId="1" pageNumber="596" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="shuichengensis">
<emphasis box="[241,402,221,244]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="596">shuichengensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<emphasis box="[464,625,221,244]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="596">shuichengehsis</emphasis>
. Acting as first revisers, we hereby select 
<taxonomicName box="[1118,1279,221,244]" class="Amphibia" family="Hynobiidae" genus="Pseudohynobius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caudata" pageId="1" pageNumber="596" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="shuichengensis">
<emphasis box="[1118,1279,221,244]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="596">shuichengensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as its correct original spelling.
</paragraph>
